  "detailed_description": "<h1>Chat with us!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/ea5fd1a64fbb86355eec5ae3b4928ded.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Link in the information block ➜</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Simulation with High Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you observe customized AI nations battle it out to ultimately try to control the world in a massive free-for-all, featuring alliances, revolts, puppet states and all kinds of political twists!<br><strong>NOTE: This is not a Strategy Game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.poster.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.webm?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.mp4?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extensive Map Creator + God Mode Tools</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game comes with premade Maps and Scenarios, but you can unleash your creativity by making your own! <u><strong>Make your maps and borders as complex as you like!</strong></u><strong> </strong>Check out <strong><u>hundreds of High Quality Scenarios on Steam Workshop</u></strong> from historical periods to fantasy worlds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.poster.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.webm?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.mp4?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Govern world history by controlling nations directly. Carefully edit borders, terrain, nation stats and AI behaviour at any point during the simulation!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World Building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View the whole History of your simulations and Statistics to get a better view of past events and nations long gone. With the right settings, the world can continue to change for thousands of years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.poster.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.webm?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.mp4?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are interested in <strong>History, Geography, Map Painting</strong> or watching chaos unfold, Ages of Conflict has got you covered!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Simulation with High Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you observe customized AI nations battle it out to ultimately try to control the world in a massive free-for-all, featuring alliances, revolts, puppet states and all kinds of political twists!<br><strong>NOTE: This is not a Strategy Game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.poster.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.webm?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.mp4?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extensive Map Creator + God Mode Tools</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game comes with premade Maps and Scenarios, but you can unleash your creativity by making your own! <u><strong>Make your maps and borders as complex as you like!</strong></u><strong> </strong>Check out <strong><u>hundreds of High Quality Scenarios on Steam Workshop</u></strong> from historical periods to fantasy worlds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.poster.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.webm?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.mp4?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Govern world history by controlling nations directly. Carefully edit borders, terrain, nation stats and AI behaviour at any point during the simulation!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World Building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View the whole History of your simulations and Statistics to get a better view of past events and nations long gone. With the right settings, the world can continue to change for thousands of years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.poster.avif?t=1772478938\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.webm?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.mp4?t=1772478938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are interested in <strong>History, Geography, Map Painting</strong> or watching chaos unfold, Ages of Conflict has got you covered!</p>",
